---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About SmartBuy Guide" 
  description="Learn about our mission to help you make informed purchasing decisions with curated Amazon product recommendations."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-800 mb-8 text-center">About SmartBuy Guide</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-primary-700">
      <p class="lead mb-8">
        Welcome to SmartBuy Guide, your trusted companion in navigating the vast world of online shopping. 
        We're dedicated to helping you make informed purchasing decisions by curating the best products from Amazon.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-800 mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Our mission is simple: to save you time and money by handpicking quality products that offer the best value. 
        Every product we recommend has been carefully selected based on quality, price, and customer satisfaction.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-800 mt-8 mb-4">Why Trust Us</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
        <li>Thorough research and vetting of all recommended products</li>
        <li>Regular updates to ensure current pricing and availability</li>
        <li>Genuine customer reviews and ratings consideration</li>
        <li>Transparent disclosure of our affiliate relationship with Amazon</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-primary-600">
          As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases. This helps us maintain our site and continue 
          providing valuable recommendations to our readers. Rest assured, this doesn't affect our product selection 
          or recommendations - we always prioritize quality and value for our readers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>